description: Number of partitions of bit-interleaved numbers; partitions of n in base sqrt(2).
comments: Rearrangement of A054225 via A054238. Also can be directly derived from A054240 (bit-interleaved addition table).
example: a(6)=4 thus: {6, 4+2, 3+1, 2+1+1} all in base sqrt(2)
author: _Marc LeBrun_, Feb 07 2000
